s="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">I enjoy taking promising and unique recipes and making them better! The concept of this pie was really interesting so I made it several times, slowly honing the recipe
Tip 1: More pastry! (Or less filling) I reckon at least another half portion
Tip 2: The pie can be a little dry so I whip up some white sauce which is really easy as you already have all the necessary ingredients (although I recommend a good spoon of dijon mustard also)
Tip 3: More water to cook cabbage (another tbsp)
Tip 4: Get a really good seal on the pastry, increase the temp of the oven and cook for less time in order to keep the egg runny
Tip 4:</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div></div></div></div></div> </section></div></div> <aside class="col span4"><div id="ad-mpu-premium-1-wide" class="ad-mpu-premium-1-wide"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-1-wide" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-381bda4ba7"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-381bda4ba7", function () {var m = Drupal.GPT.buildSizeMapping([[[0,0],[]],[[770,0],[[300,250],[300,600]]]]);var s = googletag.defineSlot(Drupal.GPT.unitPath(), m.define, "ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_1_wide-381bda4ba7").defineSizeMapping(m.mapping.build()).setTargeting("pos", ["mpu_premium_1"]).addService(googletag.pubads());});</script></div></div><div id="ad-mpu-premium-2"><div class="ad ad--mpu-premium-2-wide" id="ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-b76bd325a4"><script type="text/javascript">Drupal.GPT.createSlot("ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-b76bd325a4", function () {var m = Drupal.GPT.buildSizeMapping([[[0,0],[]],[[770,0],[[300,250],[300,251]]]]);var s = googletag.defineSlot(Drupal.GPT.unitPath(), m.define, "ad-manager-ad-mpu_premium_2_wide-b76bd325a4").defineSizeMapping(m.mapping.build()).setTargeting("pos", ["mpu_premium_2"]).addService(googletag.pubads());});</script></div></div><div id="block-bbcgf-search-views-bbcgf-cc-alt-recipes" class="block block-bbcgf-search-views"><h2>Alternative recipes</h2><ul class="section-box__list"><li class="push-item push-item--ratings"><div class="push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/push_item/public/recipe_images/recipe-image-legacy-id--858_12.jpg?itok=NaKlfJVL" width="196" height="160" alt="Tuna &amp; red onion salad" title="Tuna &amp; red onion salad" /></div><h3 class="push-item__title"> <a href="/recipes/1406/tuna-and-red-onion-salad">Tuna &amp; red onion salad</a></h3><div class="push-item__ratings"> <span class="field-content"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-user-text fivestar-average-text fivestar-comb